Quickstrike:





Quickstrke was barely interested. But he sat up a little to let KitKat know 
he was listening. He learned it was important to let a female know you were 
listening, or else you may loose a friend. He watched her shoot the rock.

"Ah rather practice on th' real thing," he said, pointing his cobra arm out, 
aiming at an invisible opponet. "Ah miss th' old days of th' Beast Wars. 
There was always somethin' t' do." He paused, thinking to himself. 
Afterwards, he laughed. "Listen t' me, ah sound like uh old rusted 
Decepticon!"
